# Local dev secrets for `wrangler dev` / vite. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored)
# and fill in. For production: `wrangler secret put GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY`.
#
# The key is used server-side by the Worker (src/worker/geo.ts) for:
#   - Places API (New)   — address autocomplete
#   - Routes API         — most-direct driving distance
# Enable BOTH APIs on the key, and set Application restriction to "None"
# (the Worker calls server-to-server, so HTTP-referrer restriction would block it).
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-api-key
